      "content": "counseling doesnt fix the math. it just gives me another person to lie to about how i'm doing. i look at my bank account and i just feel... hollow. like i'm already dead, just walking around pretending. everyone else seems to have a path, even if it's hard. but for me, it's just a dead end. i'm just stuck in a cage of my own making and there's no key. i just want the noise to stop.",
